		{
			dependencies: ["7010"]
			description: [
				"The Farming for Blockheads §eMarket§r lets you buy seeds, saplings, and crop produce for §6Emeralds§r \u2014 no more hunting rare biomes for seeds."
				""
				"§7How it works:§r Place the Market in or near your farm. It stocks a catalog of purchasable crops, saplings, and farming items. Pay with Emeralds to get anything you're missing."
				""
				"§7Emerald sources:§r Trade with villagers, loot structures, or mine Emerald Ore in mountain biomes. A few stacks of Emeralds goes a long way."
				""
				"§7Tip:§r The Market is especially valuable early for hard-to-find Farmer's Delight seeds like Tomatoes, Onions, and Rice."
			]
