		{
			dependencies: ["701F"]
			description: [
				"§bChef's Delight§r is a Farmer's Delight expansion adding professional kitchen recipes and specialty dishes with exceptional saturation and food buffs."
				""
				"§7Finding recipes:§r Browse §6Chef's Delight§r recipes in JEI or REI. Many meals use Farmer's Delight base ingredients combined in extra steps for superior results."
				""
				"§7Highlights:§r Chef's Delight dishes often stack saturation higher than anything else in the pack, making them worth the ingredient investment for long combat or mining sessions."
				""
				"§7Tip:§r Use the Cooking Pot and Skillet you already have. Chef's Delight builds on existing Farmer's Delight tools rather than requiring new equipment."
