			description: [
				"§bAether's Delight§r brings sky-island cuisine to your kitchen \u2014 golden confections, celestial fruits, and cloud-light snacks from the §eAether§r dimension."
				""
				"§7Getting ingredients:§r Visit the §eAether§r and collect Aether-specific crops, fruits, and plant drops. Bring them back to prepare sky-themed meals."
				""
				"§7Golden food lore:§r The Aether is a land of gold and ambrosium \u2014 and its cuisine carries that theme. Expect rarer ingredients but buffed regeneration and saturation from the finished dishes."
				""
				"§7Tip:§r Some Aether's Delight recipes use vanilla Stove and Cutting Board. Others combine Aether materials with standard Farmer's Delight components. Check JEI for the full recipe list."
